description:
It’s hard to believe that it’s been 7 years since Dylan made her debut on U/S and she’s only had 2 solo matches and has yet to win one. Today she’s here to finally get the “W”. She’s one of are tallest and Strongest wrestlers. She is a true Amazonian with luscious muscular legs that go on for days and days. Today she has a big Challenge. I we mean
BIG
Meet, Sophia Fiore. at 5’10 and 165lbs she is an honest-to-god Body builder who does personal training and nutrition. She can bench press a car and Squat a bus. She has absolutely no experience in wrestling but she’ confident that her muscles will work to her advantage. With Great Muscle comes Great responsibility. Dylan goes for an inverted head lock which Fiore doesn’t like much and scrambles to get Dylan off of her. With one swift, powerful toss, Dylan is put slammed to the mat and we call the match just before the end of round 3. Safety is a #1 concern here. The girl with the most points at the blow of the whistle takes the win. There’s a twist to the round 4 in the match. The winner shows utter physical dominance in the entire match. She feels that there is no need to be dominate in the sex. Instead the winner makes sweet sweet love to the loser. Today two great big powerful women show us a softer side to the Ultimate Surrender!
title: Two Ridiculously hot Amazons Wage a Sex War on our Mats
